{
  "stem": "753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You will say that you are the priests' relatives, that you come from a town called [NON-ENGLISH], which is in Italy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You lost in the bomb raids all your documents, all your clothing-- because we looked really dilapidated already by that time, totally impoverished, like refugees as you see them in the movies.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how we looked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew I-- I remember I had one dress that was lengthened and lengthened with pieces and more pieces, more pieces.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how I-- and wooden shoes, wooden clogs I had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe a little bag or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No suitcases.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- we left our suitcases in that first village in Possagno because they told us, run.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How will you run with suitcases?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had what we could carry-- knapsack, bag, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had change of underwear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember my mother [LAUGHS] had a bra that was in, in threads.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had lice because we lived in a room that they-- used to be food for animals.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there was lice a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was-- that room had mice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't-- that was a part [LAUGHS] of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I am telling you the nice part because the nice part were the people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The poverty was horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The room where we stayed in this-- in that mountain was something terrible because they, they couldn't eliminate the mice because they kept that animal food in that room that they cleaned up for us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just couldn't eliminate-- the mice was walking-- were walking all over us in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was just horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I know, even today, when I see a mouse, I scream, like, like, horror because I'm so disgusted with mice from those days.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
